subsection.p:
Adding the three sides gives
\boxed{\int_{\partial R}x\,dy=3.}
And the interior integral gives
\boxed{\int_R d(x\,dy)=\int_R dx\wedge dy=3.}
Thus
\boxed{\int_{\partial R}\omega=\int_R d\omega.}

